<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: battle axe -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.label>钺</VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.label>
  <!-- EN: A mighty weapon on the battlefield in the right kind of hands. Made to cut through flesh and bones alike.\n\nFavored by the Berserker clans, the battle axe is a weapon usually used by medieval knights. With a powerful swing it is capable of eliminating most enemies in close quarters. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.description>战斗专用的主手武器。能轻易切割血肉和骨头。\n\n这种武器深受部落狂战士的热爱，也常被中世纪骑士使用，往往只需一记强力的挥击就能永远地解决掉绝大多数的敌人。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: blade -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.tools.blade.label>钺刃</VWE_MeleeWeapon_BattleAxe.tools.blade.label>
  
  <!-- EN: halberd -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.label>长戟</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.label>
  <!-- EN: Halberd is a pike fitted with a light axe head. Due to the spear-like sharp tip, it's a great tool against armored enemies.\n\nUsed to fight down horse-mounted warriors in medieval times thanks to its its extraordinary length. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.description>长戟像是长矛和斧头的结合。擅长从好几个身位之外切开重甲目标。\n\n这种武器长度极佳，适合用来对付骑行的战士。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: blade -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.blade.label>戟刃</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.blade.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.point.label>戟尖</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Halberd.tools.point.label>
  
  <!-- EN: hammer -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.label>锤子</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.label>
  <!-- EN: A hammer is a tool that consists of a heavy piece of metal or stone at the end of a handle. It is used, for example, to hit nails into a piece of wood or a wall.\n\nThis basic invention is effective as a weapon, while being a tool at the same time. Needs some muscles to work with, but lets you construct with more ease. -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.description>由一块沉重而结实的石制或金属块连着一条把柄组成。能加快建筑效率，作为武器也十分强力，但需要较为强健的体能来挥舞它。</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.description>
  <!-- EN: handle -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.tools.handle.label>握柄</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.tools.head.label>锤头</VWE_MeleeWeapon_Hammer.tools.head.label>
  
</LanguageData>